Popular skit maker, Debo Adebayo aka Mr Macaroni, has declared he is not getting married anytime soon. The #EndSARS campaigner told an inquisitive fan on Twitter why he made the decision. The fan simply identified as Bola curious about the comedian’s plan for marriage quizzed; “Are you considering getting married anytime soon??”   Popular young Instagram skit makers working with family…     Skills determine pay in Nollywood – Biodun Stephen     Gospel singer Judikay welcomes first child   Responding to the fan, the “Freaky Freaky” crooner replied in the negative adding, he is scared of marriage. Mr Macaroni also said he hasn’t been any relationship for over a decade. “Nooooooooo!!!! Marriage scares me. I haven’t been in a relationship since my time in HNAUB … That’s like 2011-2012,” he tweeted.